snippet.title: Star Renegades- Coming to Xbox & Switch Nov. 19th
snippet.description:
Star Renegades is a dimension spanning rogue-lite strategy RPG. Outsmart uniquely generated adversaries, forge bonds between heroes and end the cycle!

Star Renegades comes to Xbox (including Game Pass) & Nintendo Switch on November 19th, followed by PlayStation 4 coming soon!

http://starrenegades.com/
